'''Alethea McGrath''' was an Australian actress who played [[Jocasta Nu]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']] and in the [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith (video game)|''Star Wars Episode III: Revenge of the Sith'']] [[Star Wars video games|video game]].

